# Mental Coach Website - Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Create a one-page branding website for a Mental Coach.
The site needs to convey **"Empathy," "Safety," and "Positive Change."**
Unlike the previous "Jet Produce" (Logic x Psychology), this site will focus purely on the **personal connection and emotional support** aspect.

## User Review Required
- **Design Vibe**: Proposing "Soft Green & Beige" (Healing/Nature) or "Warm Yellow & White" (Hope/Energy).
- **Target Audience**: Individuals seeking career change, relationship advice, or self-confidence.

